{"type": "article", "id": 21296, "title": "inbani 2016新品", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-26T08:23:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 75, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110557Ik2OzVAKBeUx5fMQ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t西班牙浴室家具公司 inbani 和巴伦西亚设计工作室 odosdesign 在他们合作的产品目录上发布了新品。卫浴与背景的颜色相近，有柔和的彩色，有大众的灰色，也有使用木质材料配合白色的背景，都显示出了居家生活的气息。其中浅粉和浅绿两款都很适合年轻人，粉色的柜子上面的洗手池像是一个圆盘，有点不稳定，俯视时圆盘超出了柜子的边界，像是几何图形叠加在一起，增添了艺术感。<a href=\"http://inbani.com/portfolio/bowl-5/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150859Vdp9uAiO7Dv2n4BF.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"804\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.98288509\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150900uCsvXdoQAw5NVEq8.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"710\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.86797066\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150900vluqRsbptdCMrVwZ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"652\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150901SujH2FKYULprC6yR.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"740\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.90464548\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150901fODx4r3oj6Fg5l1M.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1121\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.37041565\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261509025glRx8Es9ZFauYoB.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"762\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150902gRBXYNkM8ZcsojEz.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"722\" title=\" \" alt=\